SUMMARY:2741 - Empanadas Across Latin America
DESCRIPTION:Join Chef Flora Gonzalez for a flavorful journey through Latin America as you learn to craft empanadas from scratch – savory and sweet. In this hands-on class\, you will explore traditional fillings\, learn dough techniques\, and discover how one simple pastry can showcase the rich culinary diversity of the Latin world. Perfect for all skill levels and lovers of bold\, comforting flavors. \nHands on. BYOB. Ages 16 and up. \n\nBeef Picadillo Empanadas\nChicken Tinga Empanadas\nGuava and Cream Cheese Empanada
URL:https://zestchef.com/class/2741-empanadas-across-latin-america/
LOCATION:Zest Cooking School\, 1180 Erbs Quarry Road\, Lititz\, PA\, 17543\, United States
CATEGORIES:Basics and Techniques,International Cuisine,Seasonal
