SUMMARY:2742 - Kids and Teens Cooking Club: Easter Brunch
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate the flavors of spring in this fun and festive Easter Brunch class with Chef Gwen Eberly! Young chefs will learn essential cooking and baking skills while preparing a cheerful\, brunch-inspired menu perfect for sharing with family.  \nHands on. Ages 7-15. * This is a drop-off class \n\nQuiche – Bacon & Cheddar / Spinach & Feta\nCrispy Hash Browns\nBlueberry Lemon Muffins
