DESCRIPTION:Indulge in the art of French pastry with Pastry Chef Faith Kennedy in our Spring Flavors French Macarons Class! Whether you’re a baking enthusiast or simply looking to impress\, this class promises to elevate your macaron-making skills to the next level. \nHands on. BYOB. Ages 16 and up. Gluten Free Friendly* \n\nPistachio Cream Macarons\nRose Buttercream\nBlueberry Compote Macarons\nCardamom Buttercream 
