SUMMARY:2744 - Fresh Pasta 101
DESCRIPTION:You will never want to buy pasta again after chef Josh Noll takes away the mystery of making it fresh at home. With easy tips and techniques\, you’ll have the confidence needed to recreate these recipes in your own kitchen. \nHands on. BYOB. Ages 16 and up.  \n\nFresh Pasta Dough\nSpaghetti with Shrimp Scampi\nPappardelle with Mushrooms and Herbs\nSpring Salad with Citrus
