SUMMARY:2745 - Asian Dumplings
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an exciting class with Cat Alwine! Learn the art of making delicious\, handmade dumplings from scratch\, including a variety of fillings and dipping sauces. Cat will guide you through techniques for perfect folding\, steaming\, and frying\, giving you the skills to recreate these tasty treats at home. \nHands on. BYOB. Ages 16 and up. \n\nKorean Mandu\nJapanese Gyoza\nChinese Wonton Soup
