SUMMARY:2748 - Parent and Child: Spring Family Dinner
DESCRIPTION:Cook side by side in this hands-on parent and child cooking class with Chef Gwen Eberly. Families will work together to prepare a balanced\, flavorful meal while learning simple kitchen skills in a fun\, supportive environment designed for young cooks and their grown-ups. \nHands on. Ages 7 and up. Tickets are priced per person. Vegetarian friendly* \n\nSesame Salmon Squares with Orange Miso Sauce\nTurkey/Veggie Meatballs\nCreamy Asparagus and Pea Orzo\nLemon Mint Bars
