SUMMARY:2754 - Kids Cooking Club: Spring Picnic
DESCRIPTION:Let’s cook up a picnic! In this hands-on Kids Cooking Club class with Chef Gwen Eberly\, young cooks will jump right in and make some classic picnic favorites from start to finish. Along the way\, kids will practice basic kitchen skills\, try new foods\, and have fun working together in a relaxed\, encouraging environment. This class is all about building confidence\, having fun in the kitchen\, and enjoying something delicious they made themselves. \nHands on. Ages 7-15 \n\nGrilled Chicken Caesar Sandwich\nBow Tie Pasta and Veggie Salad\nChocolate Cupcakes with Strawberry Buttercream
